header(class="sticky top-0 z-20 border-b border-zinc-200 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950/95")
    div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 px-5 py-4 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between")
        div
            div(class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-layer-group")
                span 서비스
            h1(class="mt-1 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 서비스 관리
        div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
            a(routerLink="/services/create", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-plus")
                span 새 서비스
            button(type="button", (click)="load(selected()?.id || '')", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-rotate-right")
                span 새로고침

main(class="space-y-5 px-5 py-5")
    div(*ngIf="loading()", class="h-32 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-5 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400") 정보를 불러오는 중입니다.
    div(*ngIf="error()", class="rounded-md border border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-rose-700 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:bg-rose-950/40 dark:text-rose-300") {{error()}}

    div(*ngIf="!loading() && !error()", class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-5 xl:grid-cols-[380px_1fr]")
        aside(class="space-y-4")
            section(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900", data-testid="services-list")
                div(class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                    div
                        h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 서비스
                        p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 접속 주소와 실행 구성을 확인합니다.
                    span(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-600 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-300") {{services().length}}개
                div(class="divide-y divide-zinc-100 dark:divide-zinc-800")
                    button(*ngFor="let item of services()", type="button", (click)="selectService(item)", class="block w-full px-4 py-3 text-left transition-colors hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800", [ngClass]="isSelected(item) ? 'bg-sky-50 dark:bg-sky-950/30' : ''")
                        div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3")
                            div(class="min-w-0 flex-1")
                                p(class="truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{item.name}}
                                p(class="mt-1 line-clamp-2 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{serviceDescription(item)}}
                        div(class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                            span(class="inline-flex items-center gap-1")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-globe")
                                span {{servicePrimaryDomain(item)}}
                            span(class="inline-flex items-center gap-1")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-clock")
                                span {{formatDate(item.updated_at || item.created_at)}}
                    div(*ngIf="services().length === 0", class="space-y-3 px-4 py-10 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                        p 아직 서비스가 없습니다.
                        a(routerLink="/services/create", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                            i(class="fa-solid fa-plus")
                            span 첫 서비스 만들기

            a(routerLink="/services/create", class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-4 text-left hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                div
                    p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 새 서비스 만들기
                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") AI 초안이나 Compose 작성으로 필요한 설정을 준비합니다.
                i(class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-zinc-400")

        section(class="space-y-5")
            div(*ngIf="!selected() && !detailLoading()", class="rounded-md border border-dashed border-zinc-300 bg-white px-4 py-14 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400")
                p(class="font-semibold text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200") 왼쪽에서 서비스를 선택하세요.
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs") 선택하면 접속 주소, 실행 상태, 파일과 버전 이력을 확인할 수 있습니다.

            div(*ngIf="detailLoading()", class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white px-4 py-10 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400") 서비스 상세를 불러오는 중입니다.

            div(*ngIf="selected() && detail()", class="space-y-5", data-testid="service-detail")
                div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                    div(class="flex flex-col gap-4 border-b border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800 lg:flex-row lg:items-start lg:justify-between")
                        div(class="min-w-0")
                            div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                h2(class="truncate text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{detail()?.service?.name}}
                            p(class="mt-1 max-w-3xl text-sm leading-6 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300") {{serviceDescription(detail()?.service)}}
                            div(class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                a(*ngIf="primaryDomain()", [href]="domainHref(primaryDomain())", target="_blank", rel="noopener", class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-sky-200 bg-sky-50 px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-semibold text-sky-700 hover:bg-sky-100 dark:border-sky-900/70 dark:bg-sky-950/40 dark:text-sky-300 dark:hover:bg-sky-950")
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square")
                                    span {{primaryDomainText()}}
                                span(*ngIf="!primaryDomain()", class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-semibold text-amber-700 dark:border-amber-900/70 dark:bg-amber-950/40 dark:text-amber-300")
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation")
                                    span {{primaryDomainText()}}
                        div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                            button(type="button", (click)="openEditModal()", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-60 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-pen")
                                span 수정
                            button(type="button", (click)="load(selected()?.id || '')", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-60 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-rotate-right")
                                span 새로고침
                            button(type="button", (click)="deleteSelectedService()", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-rose-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-rose-700 hover:bg-rose-50 disabled:opacity-60 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:text-rose-300 dark:hover:bg-rose-950/30")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-trash")
                                span 서비스 삭제

                    div(class="grid grid-cols-1 divide-y divide-zinc-100 dark:divide-zinc-800 lg:grid-cols-4 lg:divide-x lg:divide-y-0")
                        div(class="p-4")
                            p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 실행 기준
                            p(class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{serviceStateTitle()}}
                            p(class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{serviceStateMessage()}}
                        div(class="p-4")
                            p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 접속 주소
                            p(class="mt-2 break-all text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{primaryDomainText()}}
                            p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{detail()?.domains?.length || 0}}개 연결됨
                        div(class="p-4")
                            p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 서버 / 인증서
                            p(class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{runtimeServerSummaryText()}}
                            p(class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{certificateSummaryText()}}
                        div(class="p-4")
                            p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 구성요소
                            p(class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{runtimeHealthText()}}
                            p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 전체 {{runtimeContainerSummary()?.total || 0}} · 실행 {{runtimeContainerSummary()?.running || 0}}

                    div(*ngIf="serviceIssue()", class="border-t border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 px-5 py-4 dark:border-amber-900/70 dark:bg-amber-950/30")
                        div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between")
                            div(class="min-w-0")
                                p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-200") {{serviceIssue()?.title}}
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-300") {{serviceIssue()?.message}}
                            div(class="flex flex-wrap gap-2")
                                button(type="button", (click)="refreshRuntimeStatus()", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-amber-300 bg-white px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-amber-800 hover:bg-amber-100 disabled:opacity-60 dark:border-amber-800 dark:bg-amber-950 dark:text-amber-200 dark:hover:bg-amber-900")
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-rotate-right")
                                    span 상태 다시 확인
                                button(*ngIf="serviceIssue()?.operation", type="button", (click)="openOperationModal(serviceIssue()?.operation)", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-amber-300 bg-white px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-amber-800 hover:bg-amber-100 dark:border-amber-800 dark:bg-amber-950 dark:text-amber-200 dark:hover:bg-amber-900")
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-terminal")
                                    span 처리 로그 보기
                                button(type="button", (click)="deploySelectedService()", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-amber-700 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-amber-800 disabled:opacity-60 dark:bg-amber-300 dark:text-amber-950 dark:hover:bg-amber-200")
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-rocket")
                                    span 다시 적용

                    div(*ngIf="activeBackgroundOperation()", class="border-t border-sky-200 bg-sky-50 px-5 py-4 dark:border-sky-900/70 dark:bg-sky-950/30")
                        div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between")
                            div(class="min-w-0")
                                p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-sky-800 dark:text-sky-200") 백그라운드 작업 진행 중
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-300") {{operationLabel(activeBackgroundOperation()?.type)}} · {{statusLabel(activeBackgroundOperation()?.status)}} · {{activeBackgroundOperation()?.message || '처리 로그에서 진행 상태를 확인할 수 있습니다.'}}
                            button(type="button", (click)="openOperationModal(activeBackgroundOperation())", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-sky-300 bg-white px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-sky-800 hover:bg-sky-100 dark:border-sky-800 dark:bg-sky-950 dark:text-sky-200 dark:hover:bg-sky-900")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-terminal")
                                span 작업 로그 보기

                section(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                    div(class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                        button(*ngFor="let tab of detailTabs()", type="button", (click)="setDetailTab(tab.key)", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md px-3 text-sm font-semibold transition-colors", [ngClass]="detailTab() === tab.key ? 'bg-zinc-950 text-white dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950' : 'text-zinc-600 hover:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-300 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800'")
                            i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="tab.icon")
                            span {{tab.label}}

                    div(*ngIf="detailTabLoading()", class="p-4 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 탭 정보를 불러오는 중입니다.

                    div(*ngIf="detailTab() === 'overview'", class="space-y-5 p-4")
                        section(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                            div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800 xl:flex-row xl:items-center xl:justify-between")
                                div
                                    h3(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 실행 상태
                                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 컨테이너를 외부 오픈 여부 기준으로 정리합니다.
                                div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                    p(class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{formatDate(runtimeStatus()?.checked_at)}}
                                    button(type="button", [attr.title]="runtimeBulkActionTitle('start')", (click)="runRuntimeBulkAction('start')", [disabled]="busy() || !canRunRuntimeBulkAction('start')", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-play")
                                        span 일괄 시작
                                    button(type="button", [attr.title]="runtimeBulkActionTitle('restart')", (click)="runRuntimeBulkAction('restart')", [disabled]="busy() || !canRunRuntimeBulkAction('restart')", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-rotate-right")
                                        span 일괄 재시작
                                    button(type="button", [attr.title]="runtimeBulkActionTitle('stop')", (click)="runRuntimeBulkAction('stop')", [disabled]="busy() || !canRunRuntimeBulkAction('stop')", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-rose-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-rose-700 hover:bg-rose-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:text-rose-300 dark:hover:bg-rose-950/30")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-stop")
                                        span 일괄 중지
                                    button(*ngIf="hasAiModels()", type="button", (click)="runRuntimeAiRepair()", [disabled]="runtimeAiBusy() || busy()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-sky-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-sky-700 hover:bg-sky-50 disabled:opacity-60 dark:border-sky-900/70 dark:text-sky-300 dark:hover:bg-sky-950/30")
                                        i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="runtimeAiBusy() ? 'fa-spinner fa-spin' : 'fa-wand-magic-sparkles'")
                                        span AI 검사/수정
                                    button(type="button", (click)="refreshRuntimeStatus()", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-60 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                        i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="busy() ? 'fa-spinner fa-spin' : 'fa-rotate-right'")
                                        span 상태 확인
                            div(*ngIf="runtimeContainers().length === 0", class="border-t border-zinc-200 px-4 py-8 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-400") 실행 중이거나 기록된 컨테이너가 없습니다.
                            div(*ngIf="runtimePublicContainers().length > 0", class="border-t border-zinc-200 px-4 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
                                div(class="mb-3 flex items-center justify-between gap-3")
                                    div
                                        h4(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 외부에 오픈되는 컨테이너
                                    span(class="rounded-md border border-sky-200 bg-sky-50 px-2 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-semibold text-sky-700 dark:border-sky-900/70 dark:bg-sky-950/40 dark:text-sky-300") {{runtimePublicContainers().length}}개
                                div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 xl:grid-cols-2")
                                    div(*ngFor="let container of runtimePublicContainers()", class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 shadow-sm transition hover:border-sky-200 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                                        div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3")
                                            div(class="flex min-w-0 items-start gap-3")
                                                span(class="mt-0.5 inline-flex h-9 w-9 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-sky-200 bg-sky-50 text-sky-700 dark:border-sky-900/70 dark:bg-sky-950/40 dark:text-sky-300")
                                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-globe")
                                                div(class="min-w-0")
                                                    div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                                        p(class="truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{containerDisplayName(container)}}
                                                        span(class="shrink-0 rounded-md border px-2 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-semibold", [ngClass]="containerExposureClass(container)") {{containerExposureLabel(container)}}
                                                    p(class="mt-1 truncate text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{container.node_name || '서버 확인 필요'}}
                                            div(class="flex shrink-0 items-center gap-2")
                                                span(class="rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="containerStatusClass(container)") {{containerStatusLabel(container)}}
                                                details(class="relative")
                                                    summary(class="flex h-8 w-8 cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-center rounded-md text-zinc-500 hover:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-400 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800 [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden")
                                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-ellipsis-vertical")
                                                    div(class="absolute right-0 z-20 mt-2 w-32 overflow-hidden rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white py-1 text-xs shadow-lg dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                                                        button(type="button", [attr.title]="runtimeContainerActionTitle(container, 'start')", (click)="runRuntimeContainerAction(container, 'start')", [disabled]="busy() || !canRunRuntimeContainerAction(container, 'start')", class="flex h-8 w-full items-center gap-2 px-3 text-left font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-40 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                                            i(class="fa-solid fa-play w-4")
                                                            span 실행
                                                        button(type="button", [attr.title]="runtimeContainerActionTitle(container, 'restart')", (click)="runRuntimeContainerAction(container, 'restart')", [disabled]="busy() || !canRunRuntimeContainerAction(container, 'restart')", class="flex h-8 w-full items-center gap-2 px-3 text-left font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-40 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                                            i(class="fa-solid fa-rotate-right w-4")
                                                            span 재시작
                                                        button(type="button", [attr.title]="runtimeContainerActionTitle(container, 'stop')", (click)="runRuntimeContainerAction(container, 'stop')", [disabled]="busy() || !canRunRuntimeContainerAction(container, 'stop')", class="flex h-8 w-full items-center gap-2 px-3 text-left font-semibold text-rose-700 hover:bg-rose-50 disabled:opacity-40 dark:text-rose-300 dark:hover:bg-rose-950/30")
                                                            i(class="fa-solid fa-stop w-4")
                                                            span 중지
                                                        button(type="button", [attr.title]="runtimeContainerActionTitle(container, 'delete')", (click)="runRuntimeContainerAction(container, 'delete')", [disabled]="busy() || !canRunRuntimeContainerAction(container, 'delete')", class="flex h-8 w-full items-center gap-2 px-3 text-left font-semibold text-rose-700 hover:bg-rose-50 disabled:opacity-40 dark:text-rose-300 dark:hover:bg-rose-950/30")
                                                            i(class="fa-solid fa-trash w-4")
                                                            span 삭제
                                        div(*ngIf="containerPortLabels(container).length > 0", class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-1.5")
                                            span(*ngFor="let port of containerPortLabels(container)", class="inline-flex rounded-md border border-sky-200 bg-sky-50 px-2 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-semibold text-sky-700 dark:border-sky-900/70 dark:bg-sky-950/40 dark:text-sky-300") {{port}}
                            div(*ngIf="runtimeInternalContainers().length > 0", class="border-t border-zinc-200 px-4 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
                                div(class="mb-3 flex items-center justify-between gap-3")
                                    div
                                        h4(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 내부에서만 도는 컨테이너
                                    span(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 px-2 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-semibold text-zinc-600 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-300") {{runtimeInternalContainers().length}}개
                                div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 xl:grid-cols-2")
